d 'TABBIT': module to produce sets of weighted and unweighted crosstabulation tables 
d
d    tabbit produces sets of weighted and unweighted
d crosstabulation tables and writes them directly to Excel using
d Stata’s putexcel command. It is designed for survey researchers
d who need fast, consistent production of large numbers of
d breakdown tables across many outcome and stratifier variables.
d The command handles weighted percentages, unweighted counts, row
d or column distributions, optional disclosure control, multiple
d sheets, and transparent reporting of missing values. It supports
d automated report production for survey waves, countries, sample
d groups, or exploratory analysis workflows. 
d
d KW: crosstabulations
d KW: data management
d KW: Excel
d
d Requires: Stata version 15
d
d Distribution-Date: 20251212
d
d Author: Siobhan McAndrew,  Sheffield Methods Institute, University of Sheffield
d Support: email siobhan.mcandrew@@gmail.com 
d
f tabbit.ado
f tabbit.sthlp
